oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Even Though - Harry Hanson performance
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Performance of Even Though [unconfirmed] and performed by Harry Hanson. Performance of I Miss You Already (And You're Not Even Gone), written by Marvin Rainwater and Faron Young, and performed by Faron Young. Most likely commercial recording of I Miss You Already (And You're Not Even Gone).
